In October 2017 and March 2019, the Web3 Foundation&nbsp;<a href="https://www.sec.gov/edgar/search/#/q=polkadot&amp;dateRange=all&amp;filter_ciks=0001720805&amp;filter_entityName=Web%25203.0%2520Technologies%2520Foundation%2520%2520(CIK%25200001720805)" data-v-f87c67ca="">reported</a> sales of Polkadot SAFTs under Reg. D, which reserves sales for accredited investors. The Polkadot network did not reach its final launch until last December.<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
The current&nbsp;<a href="https://coinmarketcap.com/currencies/polkadot-new/" data-v-f87c67ca="">market cap</a>&nbsp;for DOT is just under $8 billion.&nbsp;
